SUMMARY:Greenwood North - After Work Hike\, Intermediate
DESCRIPTION:GTA Hiking & Stuff\nOur first After Work hike of the season. T
 his will be a faster hike. We will hike at a moderate pace for 5 - 6 km in
  2 hrs or less. I have moved this hike to April 14th as this hiking trail 
 may still have some icy sections. Bring along your ice cleats just in case
  there is more ice than expected. We should be done before nightfall but a
  flashlight may be a good idea as well. Lets start getting in shape for su
 mmer.\n\nThe trail weaves through the forest and along a creek. There will
  be twists and turns and ups and downs but nothig serious. This event is a
 bout enjoying a hike at night.\n\n**Note**\n• Arrive on time! Don't let 
 the group wait for you.\n• Know your limits! Hike within it!\n• Dress 
 for the conditions.\n• Free Parking\n• No Dogs\n• The hike will be c
 anceled if the weather doesn't cooperate.\n\n***Hike leaves promptly at 5:
 37 PM***\n\nHope to see you there!\n\n**LEGAL DISCLAIMER AND LIABILITY INF
